extends BaseAclfBusImpl<OpfGen,AclfLoad>
implements OpfBus
    An implementation of the model object 'Base Opf Bus'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • LMP
    • PL Inequ Multiplier
    • PU Inequ Multiplier
    • QL Inequ Multiplier
    • QU Inequ Multiplier
